      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四兵卒引王翦同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00002",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "王翦"
      ],
      "text": "可恨燕孙膑，私下天台山。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00003",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "报子上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00004",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "报子"
      ],
      "text": "报！启元帅：垂莲洞毛道仙求见。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00005",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王翦"
      ],
      "text": "摆队相迎。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00006",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "报子"
      ],
      "text": "哦。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00007",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖牌子〗。王翦、四兵卒同下。毛蕡上，王翦、四兵卒同上。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00008",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "同笑",
      "speakers": [
        "王翦",
        "毛蕡"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00009",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王翦、毛蕡同下，四兵卒同下。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00010",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王翦、毛蕡同上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00011",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王翦"
      ],
      "text": "师兄下山，小弟失迎，多有慢待，师兄恕罪。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00012",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "毛蕡"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢。但不知因何免战高悬？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00013",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王翦"
      ],
      "text": "师弟被孙膑，杀得大败，因此免战高悬。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00014",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "毛蕡"
      ],
      "text": "待师兄出马，与师弟报仇。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00015",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王翦"
      ],
      "text": "孙膑法力高强，恐怕难以取胜。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00016",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "毛蕡"
      ],
      "text": "师弟呀！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00017",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "毛蕡"
      ],
      "text": "师弟休要小看咱，师父赐宝来下山。此去若遇燕孙膑，叫他一命丧黄泉。辞别贤弟去交战，",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00018",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "毛蕡下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00019",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王翦"
      ],
      "text": "等候师兄得胜还。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00020",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王翦下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00021",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孙燕上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00022",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "孙燕"
      ],
      "text": "领了军令到阵前，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00023",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙燕"
      ],
      "text": "俺，孙燕。奉了三叔将令，前到秦营讨战，探看敌人动静，就此马上加鞭。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00024",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "孙燕"
      ],
      "text": "杀却王翦报仇冤。一马来在战场上，那旁来了将一员。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00025",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "毛蕡上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00026",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "毛蕡"
      ],
      "text": "催马坐骑紧加鞭，又见娃娃到阵前。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00027",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "毛蕡"
      ],
      "text": "马前来的小将，通上名来，好在你道爷剑下做鬼！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00028",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙燕"
      ],
      "text": "妖道听者：你少爷名唤孙燕。你这野道，快快通名受死！",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001048_e00029",
      "play_id": "02001048",
      "scene_id": "02001048_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
